data.description: Cute house in great neighborhood just one street away from the lake. Great curb appeal with vinyl siding and large shade trees. Concrete driveway large enough for 6+ cars and a 2 car garage with automatic opener.  Oversized utility room would make a nice craft room or home office. The house has 3 large covered porches and fenced backyard. The interior is in good shape but in need of updates which is reflected in the list price. All electric and located in Mabank ISD.
